</tr>
<tr>
<th>Publication</th>
<th>Score</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><i><a href="/wiki/Edge_(magazine)" title="Edge (magazine)">Edge</a></i></td>
<td>7 of 10</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><i><a href="/wiki/Electronic_Gaming_Monthly" title="Electronic Gaming Monthly">Electronic Gaming Monthly</a></i></td>
<td>9.0 of 10</td>
</tr>
<tr>
